    "AboutTopTitle": "Corporate Data",
    "AboutTopHeadline": "We meet diverse needs and support global manufacturing through our high levels of quality.",
    "AboutTopBody": "We maintain a strong customer focus and provide solutions as only we can.The SATAKE Group uses the reliable quality of its in-house factory and its wide network of collaborating manufacturers, promising the best coordination and the ultimate in support.",
